            {
                "content": "```\nInput: n = 3, trust = [[1,3],[2,3],[3,1]]\nOutput: -1\n```"
            }
        ]
    },
    "readme_constraints": "- 1 <= n <= 1000\n- 0 <= trust.length <= 10^4\n- `trust[i].length == 2`\n- All the pairs of `trust` are **unique**.\n- `ai != bi`\n- 1 <= ai, bi <= n",
